        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>No Red and Blue Banks Act</b></p> <p>This bill prohibits the General Services Administration from awarding a contract to a bank or savings association insured by the Federal Deposit Insurance Corporation if the institution avoids doing business with companies based solely on social policy considerations.</p>]]>
        </text>
